summary:
I like this mod but I have some beef with it.
It's either you have to find the Cube in a place that's ridiculously hard to find (I seriously can't find that place)
or I have it right away but I have a ridiculous amount of items... there is no middle ground.

That's why I edited it.
descriptionHtml:
I edited the version where you have the cube right away but now the only items in there are 500 gold and 100 lockpicks.

I'm just a kid who wants to change the mod a little bit to his tastes and figured someone else may like it this way.

Credits to YsCordelan, the one who made the mod.
author: YsCordelan
